divs: Sighting DetailsStanding in our garage getting a soda, looking off into the horizon I noticed a pulsating light at approximatly 11:55 p.m. off in distance where flight path is over Los Angeles, Long Beach way. Light was moving to slow to be plane and pulsating various colors. I tried to get another witness but when I went to see if the object was still there, it floated up into the heavens.
